This is your new Play application
=================================

This file will be packaged with your application when using `activator dist`.

There are several demonstration files available in this template.

Controllers
===========

UserController

A sample controller that performs REST API on a User entity object.

To run the project 

a) Install activator from playframework.com
b) Run activator clean compile
c) Run activator run

Example APIs

http://localhost:9000/user GET to get all users
		    /user/{id} GET to get a user
                    /user POST to create a user
                   /user PUT to update a user
                   /user/{id} DELETE to delete a user

Requests can be tested in Postman

Example create JSON

{
  "firstName" : "test",
  "lastName" : "test",
  "age" : 10
}
 
